patthana14.34:1.1: Niyyānikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naniyyāniko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana14.34:2.1: Aniyyānikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naniyyāniko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)
patthana14.34:3.1: Niyyānikañca aniyyānikañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naniyyāniko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana14.34:4.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… vipāke ekaṃ …pe… avigate pañca.
